sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant ServicesUI as Services Dashboard
    participant ServiceAPI as /api/services endpoints
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    Admin->>ServicesUI: Open /dashboard/services
    ServicesUI->>ServiceAPI: GET /api/services
    ServiceAPI->>DB: Query OFFERING and TESTIMONIAL
    DB-->>ServiceAPI: Offerings and testimonials
    ServiceAPI-->>ServicesUI: Composite response
    ServicesUI-->>Admin: Render offerings and testimonials lists

    Admin->>ServicesUI: Create or update offering
    ServicesUI->>ServiceAPI: POST or PATCH /api/services/offerings
    ServiceAPI->>DB: Persist offering data
    DB-->>ServiceAPI: Persisted offering
    ServiceAPI-->>ServicesUI: Success

    Admin->>ServicesUI: Create or update testimonial
    ServicesUI->>ServiceAPI: POST or PATCH /api/services/testimonials
    ServiceAPI->>DB: Persist testimonial data
    DB-->>ServiceAPI: Persisted testimonial
    ServiceAPI-->>ServicesUI: Success

    Admin->>ServicesUI: Delete offering or testimonial
    ServicesUI->>ServiceAPI: DELETE endpoint call
    ServiceAPI->>DB: Delete target record
    DB-->>ServiceAPI: Delete result
    ServiceAPI-->>ServicesUI: Success
